Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:18.85,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}Přetváření Nudného Světa na Zajímavý
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:50.86,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,475)}Silver Soul Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:52.12,Main,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,No need to let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:53.91,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Do Something Uncharacteristic,\Nand Something Uncharacteristic Will Happen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:59.04,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,Cruelty reigns on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:59.04,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,with one tragedy after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:04.50,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,Wring out every last ounce of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:04.50,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,to put an end to it all!